useractor notenemy 20158 state CUSTOM_HEAL_OBJECT enda

spriteshadow 20159
useractor notenemy 20159 state CUSTOM_HEAL_OBJECT enda

spriteshadow TWENTYFIVEKIT
useractor notenemy TWENTYFIVEKIT state CUSTOM_HEAL_OBJECT enda

spriteshadow SIXPAK
actor SIXPAK state CUSTOM_HEAL_OBJECT enda

spriteshadow COLA
actor COLA state CUSTOM_HEAL_OBJECT enda

